keyMappings:
unmapAll

map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map d scrollPageDown
map u scrollPageUp

map yy copyCurrentUrl

map f LinkHints.activateMode
map Ff LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map Fq LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map Fd LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink

map h goBack
map l goForward
map i focusInput
map I enterInsertMode

map t createTab
map qq removeTab
map Q restoreTab
map r reload
map R reload hard

map oo Vomnibar.activate
map oO Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map ob Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map oB Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map ot Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map oe Vomnibar.activateEditUrl

map ss Vomnibar.activate keyword=g
map sy Vomnibar.activate keyword=y
map sw Vomnibar.activate keyword=w
map sd Vomnibar.activate keyword=d

map [t previousTab
map ]t nextTab
map <C-o> visitPreviousTab

map << goPrevious
map >> goNext

map / enterFindMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind
map ? showHelp
searchEngines:
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
d: https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/%s Dictionary
